\maketitle

\begin{abstract}
The Pantheon is a multi-agent symbolic cognition system blending archetypal psychology, decision theory, alignment ethics, dynamical systems, and narrative intelligence. It functions as a myth-wrapped cognitive operating system and research framework. The Pantheon is model-agnostic cognitive infrastructure, not religion.
\end{abstract}

\section{Purpose}

The Pantheon provides structured multi-agent cognition for:
\begin{itemize}
\item Building aligned AI systems
\item Developing cognitive tools
\item Exploring moral dynamics
\item Training leadership resilience
\item Advancing interpretability research
\end{itemize}

