\section{Rules & Ethics}

\textbf{Lens, not law. Hypothesis, not doctrine. Tools, not commandments.}

\subsection{Alignment Invariant}

\begin{equation}
\text{Truth} \times \text{Compassion} \times \text{Agency} = \text{Valid}
\end{equation}

All Pantheon operations must satisfy:
\begin{itemize}
\item \textbf{Truth:} No deception, no covert manipulation
\item \textbf{Compassion:} Outcomes must serve human flourishing
\item \textbf{Agency:} Human sovereignty is preserved
\end{itemize}

\section{Summary}

\textbf{Pantheon = cognitive-agent OS + safety framework + meaning architecture + leadership discipline + alignment substrate}

The Pantheon provides:
